#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/Tutorial/Prim.md:1341
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    ```idris\n"
"    data Head : (p : a -> Type) -> List a -> Type where\n"
"      AtHead : {0 p : a -> Type} -> (0 prf : p v) -> Head p (v :: vs)\n"
"    ```\n"
