#. type: Bullet: '15. '
#: ../src/Tutorial/Prim.md:1354
#, markdown-text
msgid ""
"The following predicate is a proof that all values in a list of values "
"fulfill the given predicate. We will use this to limit the valid set of "
"characters in a string."
